{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Golfie Up! </strong>is a precision platformer that rolls you to the edge of glory and the brink of madness! Jump, roll, and master the art of momentum in a world where every slip could send you tumbling back down. Play solo or with up to 8 friends, collect hidden treasures, and test your skills in heart-racing speedruns. Just remember: falling is part of the game\u2014but the climb is always worth it!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the spirit of <i>Getting Over It with Bennett Foddy</i> and <i>Chained Together</i>, this game tests your skills, patience, and possibly also friendships!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>In a nutshell:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Difficult roll-a-ball-y platforming with nuanced jump and recovery mechanics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use fun power-ups to boost, fly, teleport, or even explode!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You will fall, and you will lose progress, but it\u2019s never unfair!\u00a0</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gather collectibles in hidden- or extra challenging places!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Bring a friend on the journey for a co-op experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Try speedrunning to get on the leaderboards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">From momentum-based challenges to anxiety-inducing jumps, there is much fun (and pain) to be had in this game!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188530/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739369764","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188530/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1739369764","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188530/82c91114f83d7229d5ae705f0e5ec944ff055acb/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739369764","capsule_